title: Player Attack S03E21 720p HDTV h264-Berg
description:
This week, after (some of) the E3 dust has settled, we're right back looking at video games. If you're still on the fence about Batman: Arkham Knight, Jonny Robot caught up with Sefton Hill from Rocksteady Studios to talk about the big, black bat's latest outing.

We also found out all about the Diablo content that's being added to Heroes of the Storm from a couple of helpful Blizzard developers, and Jackson seems to have something else on his mind while he tells us all about Nintendo's squid/kid hybrid, Splatoon
